            "read_more": true,
            "icon_description": "",
            "description_expanded": true,
            "title_1": "Benefits",
            "icon_name_1": "",
            "raw_content_1": "<ul><li>Functions as makeup remover, facial cleanser, body wash, hand soap, bubble bath, and shaving gel for all your cleansing needs</li><li>Appropriate for all skin types</li><li>Removes dirt, SPF, makeup and impurities</li><li>Cleanses without stripping or drying skin</li><li>pH balanced to maintain skin’s natural acidity and reinforce skin’s barrier </li><li>EU compliant, clean fragrance is tested to be safe on sensitive skin </li></ul>",
            "title_2": "Key Ingredients",
            "icon_name_2": "",
            "raw_content_2": "<ul><li>Baby-safe surfactants- gentle foaming agents to cleanse </li><li>Aloe- antioxidant-rich natural humectant to soothe</li><li>Glycerin- humectant to hydrate and soothe</li><li>Gntl Signature Fragrance- a sweet, green, gender-neutral scent developed to be safe for sensitive skin </li></ul><p></p><p>Full ingredients: </p><p>Water (Aqua), Sodium Methyl Oleoyl Taurate, Sodium Lauroyl Methyl Isethionate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Lauryl Glucoside, Coco-Glucoside, Fragrance (Parfum), Glycerin, Sodium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Linalool, Limonene, Geraniol, Citral.</p>",
            "title_3": "How to Use",
            "icon_name_3": "",
            "raw_content_3": "<p>Apply to wet hands, washcloth, or loofa and massage lather onto damp skinRinse thoroughly with warm water. </p><p>Skin Wash is tough enough to remove daily makeup and SPF, but if you wear waterproof mascara, consider using an oil-based cleanser, then follow with Skin Wash. </p>",
            "title_4": "Packaging",
            "icon_name_4": "",
            "raw_content_4": "<p>Skin Wash is housed in aluminum bottles, a material that is infinitely recyclable. It features a food-grade liner that serves as an alternative to typical BPA liners, ensuring the product remains safe and stable.</p><p>The pump is the only component that cannot be recycled, so please treat it with care by refilling and reusing your bottle multiple times before recycling.</p><p>Our refill pouch is made with minimal material from a bio-based, carbon negative source that's recyclable in your local #4 stream, making our entire packaging system environmentally responsible from start to finish.</p>",
            "title_5": "",
            "icon_name_5": "",
            "raw_content_5": "",
            "padding_bottom": 20
          }
